    var data = JSON.parse(json);
    // 路径起始点
    var x = 0
    var y = 0
    // 角度
    // 0- 355
    var angle = 300
    angle = angle * 10
    // 字符间隔
    var spacing = 5

    var paths = []
    var pathWidth = 0
    var currentX = x
    var charNum = data.data.records.length
    for (const record of data.data.records) {
        const p = new fabric.Path(record.path, {fill: '', stroke: data.data.pathColor, objectCaching: false});
        p.set({left: currentX, top: y});
        if (p.width > pathWidth){
            pathWidth = p.width
        }
        currentX = currentX + p.width + spacing
        paths.push(p)
    }
    // 文字宽度
    var textWidth = currentX - x
    // 圆的半径
    var radius = ((360/angle)*textWidth)/2*Math.PI
    // 字符宽度
    var charWidth = textWidth/charNum

    if (angle !== 0){
        // 相邻字符角度差
        // var fixedLetterAngle=((charWidth)/radius)/(Math.PI/180);
        // 起始角度
        var curAngle = -(((textWidth/2)/radius)/(Math.PI/180));
        console.log("textWidth", textWidth)
        console.log("radius", radius)
        console.log("charWidth", charWidth)
        console.log("startAngle", curAngle)
        var i = 0;
        for (let path of paths) {
            let angleRadians=curAngle*(Math.PI/180);
            let top = -1*(Math.cos(angleRadians)*radius)
            let left = (Math.sin(angleRadians)*radius)
            console.log(`i:${i++}, angle: ${curAngle}, angleRadians: ${angleRadians}, top:${top}, left:${left}`)
            path.set('angle',curAngle);
            path.set('top', top);
            path.set('left', left);
            path.set('padding', 0);
            path.set('selectable', false);
            let letterAngle = ((path.width + spacing)/radius)/(Math.PI/180);
            curAngle=((curAngle)+letterAngle);
        }

    }


    var group = new fabric.Group(paths, {
        left: 10,
        top: 100,
        selectable: true
    });
    canvas.add(group)
    console.log(group.width)
    const p = new fabric.Path(data.data.path, {fill: '', stroke: 'black', objectCaching: false});
    p.set({left: 50, top: 300});
    console.log(p.width)
    canvas.add(p);
